<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SAT Test Center</title>
  
  <style>
    /* --- SEPIA ACADEMIC THEME --- */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4ecd8; /* Sepia base */
      font-family: 'Minion Pro', Georgia, serif;
      color: #4a3a2a; /* Dark brown text */
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
      padding-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #dcd3be;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #4a3a2a;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #6b5a4a;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .category-section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #8b4513;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    /* --- SCALABLE GRID SYSTEM --- */
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      /* Automatically adjusts columns based on screen size */
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background-color: #ede0d4;
      border: 1px solid #dcd3be;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
    }

    /* Hover effect for interactivity */
    .card:hover {
      background-color: #e6d5c3;
      border-color: #9c6644;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(74, 58, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
      color: #4a3a2a;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #6b5a4a;
      margin: 0;
      flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .card-footer {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #9c6644;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Welcome to the Test Center</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Select a module below to begin your SAT preparation.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="category-section">
      <h2>Practice Modules</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        
        <a href="sat-sentence-boundaries.html" class="card">
          <h3>Sentence Boundaries</h3>
          <p>Master punctuation, clauses, and essential grammar structures.</p>
          <div class="card-footer">Start Practice &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="central-ideas-and-details.html" class="card">
          <h3>Central Ideas & Details</h3>
          <p>Practice identifying main arguments and supporting evidence.</p>
          <div class="card-footer">Start Practice &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="sat_text_completion.html" class="card">
          <h3>Text Completion</h3>
          <p>Test your vocabulary in context and logical sentence flow.</p>
          <div class="card-footer">Start Practice &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="sat_standard_english_mixed.html" class="card">
          <h3>Mixed Review</h3>
          <p>A comprehensive mix of Standard English conventions.</p>
          <div class="card-footer">Start Practice &rarr;</div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="category-section">
      <h2>Reference Materials</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        
        <a href="SAT-reading-prep-cheat-sheet.html" class="card">
          <h3>Reading Cheat Sheet</h3>
          <p>Core strategies, function words, and wrong answer types.</p>
          <div class="card-footer">View Guide &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a href="sat_grammar_prep.html" class="card">
          <h3>Grammar Cheat Sheet</h3>
          <p>Essential rules and formulas for the Writing section.</p>
          <div class="card-footer">View Guide &rarr;</div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
